EN
AI automated game generator whitelist extraction process
1. Registration phase
1.1 Time frame
Registration start time: [28/03/2025]
Deadline for registration: [31/10/2025]
1.2 Enrollment Method
Users are required to create a submission folder and submission repository in the designated GitHub public repository (Repository). Submit the following content in it:
Idea description: a detailed description of your idea for an AI automated game generator, including game type, gameplay, target audience, etc.
Supporting Materials: Provide relevant images, code snippets, design sketches, or other material to demonstrate your creative direction.
Contact information: Include your e-mail address or other contact information in the README file for the repository so that we can get in touch with you.
1.3 Submission requirements
The name of the repository must be in the format of “[YourName]-AI-Game-Creator”, e.g. “JohnDoe-AI-Game-Creator”.
Ideas and materials submitted must be original or legally used materials that do not infringe on the copyright of others.
Users are required to complete their submissions by the deadline and ensure that the repository is complete and publicly accessible.

2. Information review phase

2.1 Audit Time
After the closing date of the application, we will arrange a person to review the submitted information, and the result of the review will be announced after [date of closing of the review].
2.2 Content of the audit
Data integrity: check that the repository contains creative descriptions, reference material and contact information.
Idea quality: assess the creativity, feasibility, and fit of the idea with the AI automated game generator.
Material Legitimacy: Confirm whether the submitted material is original or has been legally authorized.
Duplicate check: If the content of multiple repositorys is found to be highly similar or duplicated, the relevant user will be disqualified.
2.3 Feedback results
Audited users will be entered into the whitelist candidate pool and the list will be published.
3. Extraction phase
3.1 Extraction time
On [specific date], whitelist extraction will be conducted among all audited users.
3.2 Method of extraction
Use a randomized algorithm or random selection tool to ensure fairness and randomness in the extraction process.
If a user submits a particularly good idea, it may be prioritized (a certain percentage of “idea priority slots” is to be set).
3.3 Number of extraction
According to the testing requirements, the number of whitelisted users to be extracted is [x].

4. Publication of results phase
4.1 Publication time
The results will be announced on [specific date] after the draw.

4.2 Publication channels
Post the winner’s list in the GitHub repository.
Notify the winning user by email or SMS.
Post an announcement on the program’s official website or social media platforms.

4.3 Notification Content
Inform the winning user of the trial qualification and provide trial guidelines (e.g. download link, trial time, feedback method, etc.).

5. Follow-up phase
Unwinning users
A thank you letter is sent to non-winning users to inform them of follow-up activities and encourage them to stay tuned.
Data archiving
Archive all submissions and extraction results for subsequent reference.

CN
AI自动游戏生成器白名单抽取流程
1. 报名阶段
1.1时间范围
报名开始时间：【28/03/2025】
报名截止时间：【30/10/2025】
1.2报名方式
用户需在指定的GitHub公开仓库（Repository），创建资料文件夹和资料仓库。在其中提交以下内容：
创意描述：详细说明你对AI自动游戏生成器的创意，包括游戏类型、玩法、目标受众等。
参考素材：提供相关的图片、代码片段、设计草图或其他素材，以展示你的创意方向。
联系方式：在仓库的README文件中注明你的邮箱地址或其他联系方式，以便我们与你取得联系。
1.3提交要求
仓库名称需以“[YourName]-AI-Game-Creator”格式命名，例如：“JohnDoe-AI-Game-Creator”。
提交的创意和素材需为原创或合法使用的素材，不得侵犯他人版权。
用户需在截止日期前完成提交，并确保仓库内容完整且可公开访问。

2. 资料审核阶段

2.1审核时间
报名截止后，我们将安排专人对提交的资料进行审核，审核结果将在[审核结束日期]后公布。
2.2审核内容
资料完整性：检查仓库中是否包含创意描述、参考素材和联系方式。
创意质量：评估创意的创新性、可行性以及与AI自动游戏生成器的契合度。
素材合法性：确认提交的素材是否为原创或已获得合法授权。
重复性检查：若发现多个仓库内容高度相似或重复，将取消相关用户的资格。
2.3反馈结果
审核通过的用户将进入白名单候选池，并进行名单公布。
3. 抽取阶段
3.1抽取时间
[具体日期]，在所有审核通过的用户中进行白名单抽取。
3.2抽取方式
使用随机算法或抽奖工具，确保抽取过程的公平性和随机性。
若用户提交的创意特别优秀，可能会被优先考虑（可设置一定比例的“创意优先名额”）。
3.3抽取数量
根据测试需求，本次抽取的白名单用户数量为[X]名。

4. 公布结果阶段
4.1公布时间
抽取结束后，结果将在[具体日期]公布。

4.2公布渠道
在GitHub仓库中发布中奖名单。
通过邮件或短信通知中奖用户。
在项目官网或社交媒体平台发布公告。

4.3通知内容
告知中奖用户试用资格，并提供试用指南（如下载链接、试用时间、反馈方式等）。

5. 后续处理阶段
未中奖用户
向未中奖用户发送感谢信，告知后续活动信息，并鼓励他们继续关注。
数据存档
将所有提交的资料和抽取结果存档，以备后续查询。
